 citizenship as soon as ONE of the five commie judges dies or retires.\r\n\r\nThe future is actually very bright if you\u2019re not a raging faggot who ignores how far we have come under Trump. Things are SO MUCH better than they were in 2014.\r\n\r\nWe may actually look back in 2032 and think \u201cwow. That birthright citizenship decision actually worked to our benefit. It increased turnout and handed us a decade of wins and then we overturned it anyway.\u201d Similiar to the way overturning Roe vs Wade helped the Democrats electorally. Similiar to the way that Dems stealing 2020 actually helped us in some ways by extending the Trump Era. God works in mysterious ways. There\u2019s always silver linings if you look for them and don\u2019t doom.\r\n\r\nSign up for TPUSA and help Trump win the midterms if you\u2019re not a little bitch who expects Trump to do everything for you while you sit on your fat lazy ass.", "author": "STFUmuslimCUCKS", "created": 1782868147850, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "STFUmuslimCUCKS", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Republicans should win the midterms now.", "last_comment_created": 1782878380100, "content": "<p>Birthright citizenship is the perfect motivator to increase turnout in the midterms.</p>\n<p>All you have to do is tell people \u201c10% of births in the USA are from illegal alien mothers. If we don\u2019t deport them fast, our country will be conquered.\u201d</p>\n<p>We have the tools we need to win the midterms, deport the invaders, and save the country. The only question is will MAGA get off its fat lazy ass and do 1% of what Charlie Kirk did in every single election.</p>\n<p>If we win the midterms the sky is the limit. Vance is already positioned to win 2028, since democrats keep moving left and swing states are all moderate/centrist states. If we win the midterms and deliver 2 more years of MAGA wins, Vance 2028 and 2032 will be unbeatable.</p>\n<p>Guess what happens if Vance wins btw? We overturn birthright citizenship as soon as ONE of the five commie judges dies or retires.</p>\n<p>The future is actually very bright if you\u2019re not a raging faggot who ignores how far we have come under Trump. Things are SO MUCH better than they were in 2014.</p>\n<p>We may actually look back in 2032 and think \u201cwow. That birthright citizenship decision actually worked to our benefit. It increased turnout and handed us a decade of wins and then we overturned it anyway.\u201d Similiar to the way overturning Roe vs Wade helped the Democrats electorally. Similiar to the way that Dems stealing 2020 actually helped us in some ways by extending the Trump Era. God works in mysterious ways. There\u2019s always silver linings if you look for them and don\u2019t doom.</p>\n<p>Sign up for TPUSA and help Trump win the midterms if you\u2019re not a little bitch who expects Trump to do everything for you while you sit on your fat lazy ass.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 33, "score_up": 43, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2071925753550446603", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBhKAcaL", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 25, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8707655, "raw_content": "", "author": "bleeje", "created": 1782878777833, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": 